  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nIOCTL$I915_PXP_OPS will call i915_pxp_ops_ioctl to handle pxp ioctls. if \\*pxp_ops->action\\* is DOWNSTREAM_DRM_I915_PXP_ACTION_SET_SESSION_STATUS, it will call \\*pxp_set_session_status\\*. \\*params\\* is copied from userspace[1], which means \\*params\\* is under user con"
}